{"comments":"PathFrame — Frenet frame, normal, and curvature computation.\n\n## Design\nComputes local coordinate frames along curves for:\n- Camera paths (look-at direction)\n- Ribbon/tube extrusion\n- Motion along paths\n- Curvature analysis\n","declarations":[{"children":[],"comments":"Frenet-Serret frame at a point on the curve.\n\nThe frame provides a local coordinate system that follows the curve:\n- tangent: Direction of travel (T)\n- normal: Direction of curvature (N), perpendicular to T\n- binormal: B = T × N, completes the right-handed frame\n\nUsed for: camera paths, ribbon extrusion, tube geometry, motion along path.\n","info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"typeSynonym","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Record"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["position",{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Dimension","Vector","Vec3"],"Vec3"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["tangent",{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Dimension","Vector","Vec3"],"Vec3"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["normal",{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Dimension","Vector","Vec3"],"Vec3"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["binormal",{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Dimension","Vector","Vec3"],"Vec3"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"tag":"REmpty"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"k